Move to the left and stand in front of the sink on the left.
Put the bottle in the red trash can to the left of the sink.
Go right and stand in front of the sink on the right.
Pick the bottle up from the counter to the right of the sink.
Go left and turn to face the sink on the left.
Put the bottle in the red trash can to the left of the sink.

Put the spray bottle in the red bin to the right of the toilet.

Pick up the spray bottle that is on the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the dresser, then turn right and walk towards the tub, turn right to face the left sink.
Put the spray bottle in the red bin to the right of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to a red bin.
